* Hyprland CheatSheet

** Hyprctl

   List all monitors
   @code bash
   hyprctl monitor all
   @end

   Execute commands from config / test commands
   @code bash
   hyprctl keyword monitor "desc:Acer Technologies CB272 0x0381304E",preferred,auto-left,auto
   @end

   Execute process manually ( or any other keyword )
   @code bash
   hyprctl keyword exec -- waybar
   @end

** Find apps which run on XWayland

   @code bash
   xlsclients
   xwininfo
   hyprctl clients
   @end

